content:
I am trying to build the following dockerfile for the https://github.com/CVHub520/X-AnyLabeling.git repository. It should install any necessary dependencies and then run tests to confirm that installation succeeded:
# Use the official Miniconda base image  
FROM continuumio/miniconda3  
  
# Set the working directory  
WORKDIR /app  
  
# Copy the entire repository into the container  
COPY . /app/  
  
# Install the prerequisites  
RUN conda create --name x-anylabeling python=3.9 -y  
RUN /bin/bash -c "source activate x-anylabeling"  

# Install ONNX Runtime and other dependencies  
RUN pip install onnxruntime  
RUN pip install -r requirements-dev.txt  

# Run the test suite to verify the installation  
RUN pytest tests/
